p: Others phytoconstituents from Withania somnifera such as quercetin-3- O-galactosyl-rhamnosyl-glucoside ( Figure 17l), withanoside X ( Figure 16h), ashwagandhanolide ( Figure 16g), dihydrowithaferin A ( Figure 16f) and withanolide N ( Figure 16e) were investigated as promising inhibitors of Spike glycoprotein and Nsp15 endoribonuclease [ 127].
